			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Conversation with an adventurer who has been tortured. The player may or may not have participated in the torture. The adventurer is hurt, tired, and broken.&#xA;Note for mocap recording: the tortured adventurer can say most of his lines chained on a bed or free (standing up). Please record everything standing up. Cinematics will handle the lying down state." />
